<P>
   COXNET SCIHEALTH 0626 _ Cellular biologists at the University of
Georgia are hoping to find a cure for Chagas' disease and other
parasitic infections that are major sources of plant, animal and
human illnesses and deaths. (Cox News Service). 24.
