<P>
   LANDMINE-DOGS (Somerset, Texas) _ In addition to the NATO
security forces being deployed in Kosovo, a squad of specially
trained dogs is being sent into the embattled province to help in
the treacherous task of finding land mines. The owners of the Texas
company that trains the dogs say they have helped in demining
operations around the globe. By ZEKE MacCORMACK. (Photo available
on Wieck database.)
