   GAY-PARADE (San Francisco) _ Participants in the city's annual
festival of elegant excessories, now saddled with a cumbersome
moniker _ the Lesbian Gay Bisexual Transgender Pride Day Parade _
will promenade (not to mention boogie, slink and cruise) down
Market Street on Sunday. By MICHAEL DOUGAN.
