<DOCNO> NYT19990625.0140 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-25 14:53 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9489 &Cx1f; tab-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-A-LIST-THREATS-NYTSF &LR;      06-25 1840
