<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-25 19:11 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9902 &Cx1f; taf-z
s f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BIZ-ECON-COLUMN-$ADV2     06-25 0885
