<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Inspector Clouseau strikes again! Coke formula found
 &HT;    By Charles W. Holmes
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   PARIS _ The secret is out ... or is it?
</P>
<P>
   French scientists claim they now hold the clues to a mystery
that has baffled mankind for more than a century _ the formula for
Coca-Cola.
</P>
<P>
